      <data key="d1">"Jacob Marley was Scrooge's business partner and is mentioned in the context of Scrooge's past, symbolizing his former self."&lt;SEP&gt;"Jacob Marley was Scrooge's former business partner, who appears as a ghost seeking redemption."&lt;SEP&gt;"Marley was Scroodge's deceased partner, whose ghostly face appears on the door knocker, symbolizing a significant supernatural event."</data>
      <data key="d2">chunk-d9aac3484185ac66045df92214d245d5&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8f738cb25d60a7dab782162d9d0a25ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-89777b838d5447c7bd1ec11282c4ee89</data>
