      <data key="d1">"The Ghost of Christmas Present is a supernatural entity that appears to Scrooge, symbolizing the present and bringing about change."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost of Christmas Present represents a guiding figure who shows Scrooge visions related to Christmas and his past, present, and future."&lt;SEP&gt;"The Ghost of Christmas Present represents the present state of humanity, highlighting the joys and sorrows of the living. It appears to Scrooge to broaden his understanding of Christmas spirit."</data>
